Denver Broncos running back Javonte Williams (33) is tackled by Los Angeles Chargers linebacker Daiyan Henley (0) in the second half of a game on Sunday, Nov. 26, 2023, at Empower Field at Mile High in Denver, Colo. (Parker Seibold, The Gazette)

Broncos place kicker Wil Lutz kicks a field goal in the first half Sunday in Denver.
Denver Broncos quarterback Russell Wilson (3) walks the sidelines in the second half of a game on Sunday, Nov. 26, 2023, at Empower Field at Mile High in Denver, Colo. Wilson didn’t play in the Broncos’ home game of the season. (Parker Seibold, The Gazette)
